snippet.title: WHAT THE GOLF? - ☠️Failure trailer☠️ - top 5 bugs
snippet.description:
WHAT THE GOLF? - the golf game for people who hate golf.

Nintendo Switch: https://whatthegolf.com/switchstore
PC: https://store.steampowered.com/app/785790/WHAT_THE_GOLF/
Apple: http://whatthegolf.com/apple

A silly physics-based golf parody.
This game is made by people who know nothing about golf and it will NOT make you a better golfer!

Discord: http://discord.gg/triband
Website: http://whatthegolf.com
